title: Cyndi.Lauper.2013.12.09.Front.and.Center.720p.HDTV.x264-CLDD
description:
Cyndi Lauper
New York, NY
Highland Ballroom 
December 9, 2013
She's So Unusual 30th Anniversary
Recorded from the PBS television show, Front and Center.


In 2013, Cyndi Lauper did an extensive tour, playing the entire SSU album beginning to end, celebrating the 30th Anniversary. 
This was her last concert of 2013, and it was filmed.  A few more songs were played that night, but the TV broadcast is just the 10 tracks from She's So Unusual.


I am uploading 2 versions of this.  One is the the raw source (M2TS format), direct from the DVR.  Suitable to make a DVD-R if anyone feels the urge. 
I am also uploading a compressed MP4 file (x264) for people who don't need/want the full quality version. 


Stick around and seed, so people who stumble across this down the road still get a chance to see it!
